Oh - 'til she died - practically, 'cos we - we moved from there, after being there twenty-odd years - my mother - after I was married - moved to Redcar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 She had a boarding house there did she?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 And - yes, she had a place there, where the Park Hotel is now. Took a very big place there.
