\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8202628\charrsid5856546 then}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546  I was - coming up fourteen you know at that age. That - oh yes, we all helped in the house.
