No, not - in the early part. In the latter part - me father took a fancy to taking - having a few rabbits. In - when we lived in Marton Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Did you have a garden there?
