\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Not that I know of, no, not 'til - we went to Marton Road and that was the time when - we would eat more t
inned stuff you know, then. Tinned corned beef and suchlike. But when we were little - it was always fresh stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Did you ever get some extra meat such as rabbit from poaching, you told me you had rabbit, but did it ever come from poaching at all?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 No.
