\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Do you remember seeing your mother have less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 No. It was all shared alike. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Your father didn't have any more then?
