\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Did you take part in any sports at all?
