\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Well, 'cos when
 we moved - Marton Road we used to get passes and we could go to see the operas and suchlike. Yes. Yes. Yes. Go to the - the - the pantomimes and - used to - as I say, we used to get the passes to go there and they used to go and - when we had the chorus 
g
irls in I used to take their teas up when they were - they were rehearsing and suchlike, up to the - opera house where they used to have their pantomime. And - they'd say, bring us our tea and - suchlike and - I'd go and take it up and oh I was - thrilled
, that was - I was a star then. Oh I could - I could do all they were doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 You used to copy them?
