shops}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 . Yes, I was once - part time book keeper in a - fine arts sale room. One - one amusing job. And - you know, these cheap-jack - sales that you see at the seaside, where they have a }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8202628\charrsid5856546 table}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 
 and - and put your penny down you know and the come a bit further in a little to get you right in the - in the saleroom. Yes, I used to - I used to be the book keeper, but be - before I could go behind
 and - get any money we had to draw the crowd in first.
