\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Yes, and then - I went to - Scarborough and Bridlington I worked. Season jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10687487 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Was that before you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5314155 DR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4684011\charrsid5856546 Yes. Yes.
